response = self.app.post('/%s/movies/1234' % self.api, headers=self.headers,
    data=json.dumps({}), content_type='application/json')
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 405)
response_json = json.loads(response.data or '{}')
self.assertDictContainsSubset({'message':
    u'Not supported resource creation'}, response_json)
